The Telegraph - Calcutta : Bengal
 Tuesday, April 20, 2004 				 John Hughes
Calcutta, April 19: John Hughes of Goethals Memorial School, Kurseong, passed away on April 13. He was 79.																								A renowned personality in the sphere of education, Hughes had taught in several Christian Brothers schools across India during his 53 years in the country.
